name: A Mess of Unfinished Thoughts
description: a person. a morning. storm. raining after office hour. "is everything ok?". Books. Road. Rain Puddles. Random faces from the street. 3:45Am from your timezone. A message. Discomfort. Disquiet. Connected. Disconnected. Sleepless nights. Typing keyboard. "I like my coffee black". Your corporates friend. Hypocrisy. Detach. Discover.
